Description: relay2slack
        ======
        
        relay2slack is a tool for capturing and forwarding incoming Slack webhook events.
        
        
        Installation
        ------------
        To install relay2slack, simply:
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            $ pip install relay2slack
        
        To run relay2slack in the foreground:
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            $ relay2slack
        
